question: list the names of all teachers that are older than 49 and the names of all managers with a rating lower than or equal to 9 stars

SELECT store.name
FROM classes
INNER JOIN instructors ON instructors.teacher_id = classes.teacher_id
INNER JOIN store ON store.name = instructors.name
WHERE store.star_rating >= 6 AND (classes.class_subject = 'biology' OR classes.class_subject = 'sociology') AND classes.grade >= 72

SELECT instructors.name
FROM classes
INNER JOIN instructors ON instructors.teacher_id = classes.teacher_id
INNER JOIN store ON store.name = instructors.name
WHERE instructors.teacher_age >= 71 AND store.star_rating >= 2
